column5: Season Six starts tommorrow morning on OLN @ 9:30 and again at noon.  Extreme Angler TV Season Six is Loaded and Ready to go.. Who wants to wait till May to catch springtime walleye?... not Team-X...Bob Devine and Mark Kulik have a blast with a Springtime Smash Session of  Detroit River Walleye, and K-Dawg locates the beasts hiding in the green grass of Bass!  Enjoy Boys & Girls...  It's going to be Great!!  Extreme Army Team The Spikester
